Feature: syntax-error

  Scenario Outline: raise error when right operand is not schema
    When evaluate by:
    """
    is <schema>
    """
    Then failed with the message:
    """
    Expect a schema
    """
    And got the following notation:
    """
    is <schema>
       ^
    """
    Examples:
      | schema   |
      | +        |
      | (Schema) |

