  Scenario: available schema syntax
    Given the following schema class:
    """
    public class Id {
      public static class Zero {
          public int id = 0;
      }
    }
    """
    And the following json:
    """
      {
        "id": 0
      }
    """
    Then the following verification should pass:
    """
      is Id.Zero
    """

